snippet: A Houston-area teenager was sentenced Friday to 20 years in prison for the fatal stabbing of another teen during a high school cafeteria fight last year that also left three others injured....

headline.print_headline: Teen Sentenced to 20 Years for Fatal Stabbing
headline.main: Teen Sentenced to 20 Years for Fatal Stabbing

lead_paragraph: A Houston-area teenager was sentenced Friday to 20 years in prison for the fatal stabbing of another teen during a high school cafeteria fight last year that also left three others injured.
